
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8000
VITE_FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:8080
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:8080
OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://host.docker.internal:11434/api

# ── Production ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Vite inlines VITE_* vars into the static JS bundle at BUILD time (not read at
# runtime). If the site is served over https:// but VITE_API_URL is http://,
# browsers block every API call as mixed content ("Failed to fetch").
# Use the real https domains and rebuild+redeploy the frontend image whenever
# these change - restarting the container is not enough, it must be rebuilt.
#
# VITE_API_URL=https://api-nexthire.itc4d.com
# VITE_FRONTEND_URL=https://nexthire.itc4d.com
# FRONTEND_URL=https://nexthire.itc4d.com
# ALLOWED_ORIGINS=https://nexthire.itc4d.com
